node.text:
🎄@chefclubtv have created the perfect festive dessert: A Peppa Pig Christmas Charlotte 🎄 Why not give it a try with your little ones?    Ingredients: Puff pastry sheet: 1 Whipping cream: 500ml Mascarpone: 220g Icing sugar: 100g Single cream: 30ml Raspberry sauce: 250ml Sponge fingers: 16  Raspberries: 20 Redcurrent: 12 Marshmallows: 2 Chocolate buttons: 2 Red natural food colouring   Utensils: 1 Peppa Christmas cut out – Head to the Peppa Pig website to download yours 🐷🎄 1 Electric whisk 1 Large mixing bowl 2 Smaller mixing bowls 1 Freezer bag
 Optional:  Star and Christmas tree-shaped cookie cutters

🎄🎄🎄

Who else loved watching the @Olympics this year? We did! We're so inspired by @SkyBrown in the new skateboarding 🛹 category! We're going to nominate Peppa for a new category: Jumping in muddy puddles 🐽

#PeppaPig #Olympics #Tokyoy2020 #Skybrown #ClosingCeremony #Skateboarding #MuddyPuddles #GoldMedal#Olympicshumour #olympicmemes #teamGB
